title: BRIEF-Ctac extends partnership with Winshuttle to Belgium and France
text:
BRIEF-Ctac extends partnership with Winshuttle to Belgium and France Sept 8 
Sept 8 Ctac NV : 
* Extends partnership with Winshuttle to Belgium and France 
* The partnership means that Ctac's will deliver and support Winshuttle's data management platform in Belgium and France, as it does in the Netherlands Source text: bit.ly/1EMjH6m Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom) Trending On Reuters
